name: Spacious South End 2BR | Kitchen | Work Desk | GLS
description:
Experience South End, your new Home away from Home.
Offering high-end apartments with creative amenity spaces, open floor plans and furnished space, featuring a fully equipped kitchen, full windows and more.
Amenities include:
• Fully furnished w/ premium bedding
• Full kitchen w/ Stainless Steel Appliances
• Work Desk + Wi-Fi
• In-unit Washer/Dryer
• Rooftop pool & Garden
• 24 Hour Fitness Center
• On site retail & dining
• Immediate access to Orange, Red, and Silver MBTA lines
